I '''Evgeny Aramovich Abramyan''' ({{lang-ru|Евге́ний Ара́мович Абрамя́н}}; mibait [[Agostu 3]], [[1930]]) — metung a [[Soviet Union|Soviet]]/[[Russians|Russian]] physicist a atin Armenian lahi, Professor, Doctor ning Engineering Sciences, Menyambut keng [[USSR State a Galal]], metung kareng mitatag kareng dakal a papuntang pamanyalugsug keng Soviet ampong  Russian nuclear technology. Talasulat kareng maiggit a 100 imbentu ampong dakal a aklat keng applied physics.

